{"tid":249681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"崩潰！宿舍水龍頭噴出屍毛　更恐怖的在後頭","createTime":"2017-05-19T13:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T14:46:23.000Z","uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"546cbb6f75b0c05e04244021bff6f83b44aea3be","tid":249681,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:14:39.000Z","msg":"崩潰！宿舍水龍頭噴出屍毛　更恐怖的在後頭<br />\n2017/05/19 13:58 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20170519/1121841/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Flife%2F20170519%2F1121841%2F&h=809c1b87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大學宿舍的水龍頭竟有毛！男學生發現後崩潰了！<br />\n一名網友在匿名臉書《靠北中教大》吐苦水，所PO出畫面讓人捏把冷汗！因為照片中可見，淋浴的水龍頭噴出的不只是水，還有一根根的鳥毛。學生崩潰寫下「水龍頭一打開就噴一堆鳥羽毛出來，推測應該是鳥死在管線中，泡水腐爛再來羽毛脫落，然後降臨在無辜的大學生身上，幹越洗越髒，細菌含量爆表。」<br />\n<br />\n更讓人崩潰的是，不只是洗澡，就連衣服也全都「中獎」，「連洗衣間水龍頭打開都是，衣服也都遭殃」，讓網友怒吼「還我乾淨的宿舍啊！」<br />\n這畫面讓其他人看了也傻眼，「喔幹好噁」、「已吐」，還有網友說「好險不是人的」，也有網友提出更毛的，「想知道飲水機水源是？」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"57bef37273e5490202ee6ddd8e86d876e5ca108d","tid":249681,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:15:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20170519/1121841/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Flife%2F20170519%2F1121841%2F&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=24892c2f\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20170519/1121841/</a>"},{"pid":"6f7e51a6b22511d1fa29fe1dfc47d644afb98325","tid":249681,"uid":48981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:18:09.000Z","msg":"哇屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇圖打曬冷震"},{"pid":"b5bd8b68203c3fa806fdbdcb3990a4f8b93469bf","tid":249681,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:19:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哇屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇圖打曬冷震</blockquote><br />\n搞到我唔敢開嚟睇，但又好想睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebbca640ab1780b7d87ece7a4925dc3975d86075","tid":249681,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:21:44.000Z","msg":"「想知道飲水機水源是？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眼不見為淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec78539a84454d6b11f621b5977791d9546cb88","tid":249681,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:23:16.000Z","msg":"屍毛 台灣記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a38ce479ab44d0181c091e5488e0e509958db7c","tid":249681,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:39:13.000Z","msg":"下面有間清潔水喉公司回應幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be70f4cb73e7b41f2dfea231af6ce240c0d91381","tid":249681,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T14:06:06.000Z","msg":"雀姐，消毒囉，起碼唔係人"},{"pid":"a88cfa0e2c01f54417397d093c2a7c289d5fb01a","tid":249681,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T14:09:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"870a6e83194f923f50725728e365ac696f6f8662","tid":249681,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T14:46:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}